{"tid":1519433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚連登嘅沉重唔是驚左個政權！是驚聽日見唔到你地落場！","createTime":"2019-08-30T14:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:51:57.000Z","uid":167548,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9da920d3ec0ee0dfa09d7367069c052fdf8eaa06","tid":1519433,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"聽日意義好重大同關鍵！<br />\n點解？<br />\n關鍵在於聽日是第一次無大台之下靠群眾吹雞吹到有100萬人企出嚟一齊「非法集結」！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地根本唔怕呢個政權！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地只是怕聽日見唔到你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地忍心置我地於<span style=\"color: red;\">「死」</span>境嗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，無得退！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果聽日無大台吹雞都吹得到百萬行就一齊開開心心番屋企！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答應我 聽日 下午3點維園見！而且用盡你人情牌叫更加多人去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊嚟一齊走！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"795f8f07e1c76fc8c7b2c1ebe481b7fba5bb159d","tid":1519433,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=htt